{"tid":552582,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"九唔搭八香港地名競猜","createTime":"2018-02-06T15:35:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-06T16:14:48.000Z","uid":109462,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fa5af2373dc1a914b6365fada6e406860c0b394f","tid":552582,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T15:35:49.000Z","msg":"今日喺圖書館見到本大陸翻譯嘅書，赫然發現以下呢八個「香港地名」，放上嚟等大家估下呢幾個地方其實係香港邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n蒙科<br />\n沙姆蘇坡<br />\n旺差<br />\n賽印普<br />\n卡斯別<br />\n阮廊<br />\n泰波<br />\n夏丁<br />\n<br />\n呢啲地方都係大家日常有機會去到嘅地方，所以唔使諗奬門人嗰啲山卡啦地名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以上地名出處：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/06/233204_fec14cfb57ab16f856d53a4d89b98f57.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F06%2F233204_fec14cfb57ab16f856d53a4d89b98f57.png&h=772966f9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cad0477e9960c8c90568ee2d3b5cc9824d474c0a","tid":552582,"uid":82532,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T15:37:33.000Z","msg":"蒙科 = 旺角<br />\n沙姆蘇坡 = 深水埗<br />\n旺差 = 灣仔<br />\n賽印普 = 西營盤<br />\n卡斯別 = Causeway Bay<br />\n阮廊 = 元朗<br />\n泰波 = 大埔<br />\n夏丁 = 沙田"},{"pid":"cda37001bb1c49509a83dd4da340d8ba84b96e30","tid":552582,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T15:38:38.000Z","msg":"被秒"},{"pid":"10a4ea65ce71b2a35bc6743613593c99ba375d93","tid":552582,"uid":82532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T15:39:07.000Z","msg":"幾有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4b9b93f7e02a131a4bbd93181f0ebb640d425db","tid":552582,"uid":109462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cad0477e9960c8c90568ee2d3b5cc9824d474c0a","tid":552582,"uid":82532,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T15:37:33.000Z","msg":"蒙科 = 旺角<br />\n沙姆